uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.model

Class MZTabRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.model.MZTabRecord
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Peptide, Protein, PSM, SmallMolecule

    public abstract class MZTabRecord
extends Object
    MZTabRecord used to store a row record of the table. The record SHOULD keep the same structure with the MZTabColumnFactory, which defined in the construct method.
    Since:
    23/05/13
    Author:
    qingwei
    See Also:
    Protein, Peptide, PSM, SmallMolecule

      • setValue

        public boolean setValue(String logicalPosition,
               Object value)
        Set a value to a special logical position cell. Before set value, system will do a match validate by calling isMatch(String, Class). If not match, system not do set operation and return false value.
        Parameters:
        logicalPosition - locate the column data type definition in MZTabColumnFactory
        value - SHOULD NOT set null.
